summary: An experienced ICT-professional achieving outcome-driven goals, with proven ability to plan and deliver projects within budget and deadlines. Responsible for major IT change projects with major impact on the organization (Heineken, Hydron [now part of Vitens] and Van Zwol Wijntjes Accountants & Consultants. Able to explain complex change projects to management, and guidance these processes in the workplace. Possess the technical skills to perform implementations and provide standardized workstation and server environments. Results achieved are controllable ICT infrastructures with proven high availability and low cost of workstation maintenance (‘zero’ maintenance for roll-out and recovery).
